      <profileDesc>
         <abstract>
            <p>Five bighas, or a little over three acres, of tax-exempt land are allocated from the village <placeName ref="#maliwada">Maliwada</placeName> in district (pargana) <placeName ref="#pgDhar">Dhar</placeName>
               to <persName ref="#nathmal">Nathmal</persName>, son of the landlord (chaudhri) <persName ref="#purshottamDas">Purshottam Das</persName>, to plant a garden and build a resthouse for travelers. </p>
